Date: Sat, 28 Feb 2026 19:35:37 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 44/45] Add per-tab color scheme via XPC

The dark mode came knocking at the door,
"prefers-color-scheme" it was looking for.
XPC now carries dark or light,
Each tab remembers day or night.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
